# Constants and folding

Compile-time-only values and shared runtime semantics.

## Contract

- Input: constant declarations and constant-eligible expressions
- Output: folded constants, const facts and const page-fragment metadata
- Decides: what folds, const-record shape, config extraction, compile-time template folding
- Must not decide: runtime code generation, HIR control flow, backend lowering
- Invariant: compile-time folding agrees with runtime lowering

## Main paths

- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/const_eval/`
- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/module_ast/finalization/const_fact_collection.rs`

